If $f\left(x_{0}\right)>x_{0}$, then $f\left(f\left(x_{0}\right)\right)>f\left(x_{0}\right)>x_{0}$, which contradicts the condition $f\left(f\left(x_{0}\right)\right)=x_{0}$;

